---
import ImageCarousel from './ImageCarousel.astro';
---

<section id="servicos" class="services section-padding">
	<div class="container">
		<!-- Carrossel de Imagens -->
		<ImageCarousel />

		<div class="services-header">
			<h2 class="section-title">
				<span class="gradient-text">Estrutura avançada</span><br>
				para seu conteúdo
			</h2>
			<p class="section-subtitle">
				Equipamentos de última geração e ambiente profissional para transformar suas ideias em conteúdo de alta qualidade.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="services-grid">
			<div class="service-card featured">
				<div class="service-header">
					<div class="service-icon">
						<svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
							<rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
							<circle cx="8" cy="10" r="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
							<path d="M14 15L10 11L4 17H20L16 13L14 15Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
							<rect x="16" y="6" width="4" height="3" rx="1" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<div class="featured-badge">Destaque</div>
				</div>
				<h3>Estúdio Completo</h3>
				<p>Equipamentos audiovisuais profissionais com gravação e edição simultânea de 3 câmeras para máxima qualidade visual.</p>
				<ul class="service-features">
					<li>3 câmeras profissionais</li>
					<li>Gravação simultânea</li>
					<li>Edição em tempo real</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<div class="service-card">
				<div class="service-icon">
					<svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
						<circle cx="12" cy="12" r="5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
						<path d="M12 1V3M12 21V23M4.22 4.22L5.64 5.64M18.36 18.36L19.78 19.78M1 12H3M21 12H23M4.22 19.78L5.64 18.36M18.36 5.64L19.78 4.22" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
						<circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2" fill="currentColor"/>
						<path d="M8 8L16 16M16 8L8 16" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3>Iluminação LED Profissional</h3>
				<p>Sistema completo de iluminação cênica em LED, capaz de criar atmosferas variadas e imersivas para qualquer tipo de conteúdo.</p>
				<ul class="service-features">
					<li>Iluminação cênica</li>
					<li>Controle de temperatura</li>
					<li>Cenários customizáveis</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<div class="service-card">
				<div class="service-icon">
					<svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
						<path d="M12 1C18.5 1 23 5.5 23 12S18.5 23 12 23C5.5 23 1 18.5 1 12S5.5 1 12 1Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
						<path d="M8 12L11 15L16 9" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
						<path d="M12 6V8M12 16V18M6 12H8M16 12H18" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/>
						<circle cx="12" cy="12" r="1" fill="currentColor"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3>Áudio de Alta Qualidade</h3>
				<p>Captação de áudio profissional com equipamentos de última geração para garantir clareza e qualidade sonora excepcional.</p>
				<ul class="service-features">
					<li>Microfones profissionais</li>
					<li>Tratamento acústico</li>
					<li>Mixagem ao vivo</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<div class="service-card">
				<div class="service-icon">
					<svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
						<rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
						<line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
						<line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
						<path d="M6 7H18M6 11H18M6 15H12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3>Edição e Streaming</h3>
				<p>Computador dedicado para edição profissional e streaming ao vivo, com software especializado e internet de alta velocidade.</p>
				<ul class="service-features">
					<li>Edição profissional</li>
					<li>Streaming ao vivo</li>
					<li>Internet de alta velocidade</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<div class="service-card">
				<div class="service-icon">
					<svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
						<path d="M3 9L12 2L21 9V20C21 20.5304 20.7893 21.0391 20.4142 21.4142C20.0391 21.7893 19.5304 22 19 22H5C4.46957 22 3.96086 21.7893 3.58579 21.4142C3.21071 21.0391 3 20.5304 3 20V9Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
						<polyline points="9,22 9,12 15,12 15,22" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
						<path d="M7 16H17M7 19H17" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3>Ambiente Climatizado</h3>
				<p>Sala climatizada no 24º andar do Hub P7 Criativo, proporcionando conforto total e vista panorâmica de Belo Horizonte.</p>
				<ul class="service-features">
					<li>Climatização completa</li>
					<li>Vista panorâmica</li>
					<li>Ambiente profissional</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<div class="service-card">
				<div class="service-icon">
					<svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
						<path d="M14.7 6.3C16.2 7.8 17 9.8 17 12S16.2 16.2 14.7 17.7M18.4 3C21.2 5.8 23 9.8 23 14S21.2 22.2 18.4 27M9.3 17.7C7.8 16.2 7 14.2 7 12S7.8 7.8 9.3 6.3M5.6 21C2.8 18.2 1 14.2 1 10S2.8 1.8 5.6 -3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
						<circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
						<path d="M10 10L14 14M14 10L10 14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3>Suporte Técnico</h3>
				<p>Equipe técnica especializada da 4Nexus disponível durante toda a gravação para garantir qualidade e resolver qualquer questão.</p>
				<ul class="service-features">
					<li>Suporte completo</li>
					<li>Equipe especializada</li>
					<li>Assistência técnica</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="services-cta">
			<div class="cta-content">
				<h3>Ideal para diversos tipos de conteúdo</h3>
				<div class="content-types">
					<span class="content-tag">Podcasts</span>
					<span class="content-tag">Videocasts</span>
					<span class="content-tag">Cursos Online</span>
					<span class="content-tag">Entrevistas</span>
					<span class="content-tag">Conteúdo Corporativo</span>
					<span class="content-tag">Lives</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.services {
		background: white;
	}

	.services-header {
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 5rem;
	}

	.services-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 5rem;
	}

	.service-card {
		background: white;
		padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
		border-radius: 1.5rem;
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 90, 61, 0.1);
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
	}

	.service-card::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		right: 0;
		height: 4px;
		background: var(--gradient-primary);
		transform: scaleX(0);
		transition: transform 0.3s ease;
	}

	.service-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-8px);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-xl);
	}

	.service-card:hover::before {
		transform: scaleX(1);
	}

	.service-card.featured {
		background: var(--gradient-primary);
		color: white;
		transform: scale(1.02);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-xl);
	}

	.service-card.featured::before {
		display: none;
	}

	.service-card.featured:hover {
		transform: scale(1.05) translateY(-8px);
	}

	.service-header {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		align-items: flex-start;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.service-icon {
		color: var(--primary-coral);
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.service-card.featured .service-icon {
		color: white;
	}

	.featured-badge {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
		color: white;
		padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
		border-radius: 1rem;
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
	}

	.service-card h3 {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		color: inherit;
	}

	.service-card p {
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		opacity: 0.9;
		color: inherit;
	}

	.service-features {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.service-features li {
		padding: 0.5rem 0;
		position: relative;
		padding-left: 1.5rem;
		opacity: 0.8;
	}

	.service-features li::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		top: 0.75rem;
		width: 6px;
		height: 6px;
		background: var(--secondary-yellow);
		border-radius: 50%;
	}

	.service-card.featured .service-features li::before {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
	}

	.services-cta {
		background: var(--light-gray);
		padding: 4rem 3rem;
		border-radius: 2rem;
		text-align: center;
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 90, 61, 0.1);
	}

	.cta-content h3 {
		font-size: 2rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--black);
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.content-types {
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 1rem;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.content-tag {
		background: white;
		color: var(--primary-coral);
		padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 2rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		border: 2px solid var(--primary-coral);
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
	}

	.content-tag:hover {
		background: var(--primary-coral);
		color: white;
		transform: translateY(-2px);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.services-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 1.5rem;
		}

		.service-card.featured {
			transform: none;
		}

		.service-card.featured:hover {
			transform: translateY(-8px);
		}

		.services-cta {
			padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem;
		}

		.cta-content h3 {
			font-size: 1.5rem;
		}

		.content-types {
			gap: 0.75rem;
		}

		.content-tag {
			padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
			font-size: 0.875rem;
		}
	}
</style>